	<question id="2012BeijingGaokao_16_01" type="shortanswer">
	    <text format="latex">因为D,E分别为AC,AB的中点, 所以$DE\parallel BC$.又因为$DE\not\subset A_1CB$,所以$DE\parallel A_1CB$.</text>
