	<question id="2012BeijingGaokao_16_02" type="shortanswer">
	    <text format="latex">由已知得$AC\perp BC$且$DE\parallel BC$,所以$DE\perp AC$.所以$DE\perp A_{1}D$,$DE\perp CD$.所以$DE\perp A_{1}DC$.而$A_{1}F\subset A_{1}DC$,所以$DE\perp A_{1}F$.又因为$A_{1}F\perp CD$,所以$A_{1}F\perp BCDE$.所以$A_{1}F\perp BE$. 
        </text> 
	</question>
	
