	    <text format="latex,html">线段$A_{1}B$上存在点Q,使$A_{1}C\perp DEQ$.理由如下:<Picread id="Pic16_1">如图</Picread>,分别取$A_{1}C$,$A_{1}B$的中点P,Q,则$PQ\parallel BC$.又因为$DE\parallel BC$.所以$DE\parallel PQ$.所以平面DEQ即为平面DEP.由第二问知,$DE\perp A_{1}DC$,所以$DE\perp A_{1}C$.又因为P是等腰三角形$DA_{1}C$底边$A_{1}C$的中点,所以$A_{1}C\perp DP$.所以$A_{1}C\perp DEP$.从而$A_{1}C\perp DEQ$.故线段$A_{1}B$上存在点Q,使得$A_{1}C\perp DEQ.</text>
