	<question id="2012BeijingGaokao_19_02" type="shortanswer">
	    <text format="latex">由
		$$ \left\{
                   \begin{aligned}
                   y=k(x-1) \\
                   \frac{x^2}{4}+\frac{y^2}{2}=1\\
                   \end{aligned}
                   \right.
        $$
	        得$(1+2k^2)x^2-4k^2x+2k^2-4=0$.
			设点M,N的坐标分别为$(x_{1},y_{1})$,$(x_{2},y_{2})$,则$y_{1}=k(x_{1}-1)$,$y_{2}=k(x_{2}-1)$,$x_{1}+x_{2}=\frac{4k^2}{1+2k^2}$,$x_{1}x_{2}=\frac{2k^2-4}{1+2k^2}$.
			所以$|MN|=\sqrt{(x_{2}-x_{1})^2-(y_{2}-y_{1})^2}=\sqrt{(1+k^2)[(x_{1}+x_{2})^2-4x_{1}x_{2}]}=\frac{2\sqrt{(1+k^2)(4+6k^2)}}{1+2k^2}$,
			又因为点$A(2,0)$到直线$y=k(x-1)$的距离$d=\frac{|k|}{\sqrt{1+k^2}}$	,
            所以$\triangle AMN$的面积为$S=\frac{1}{2}|MN|\cdot d=\frac{|k|\sqrt{4+6k^2}}{1+2k^2}$.由$\frac{|k|\sqrt{4+6k^2}}{1+2k^2}=\frac{\sqrt{10}}{3}$,解得$k=\pm 1$.			
		</text>
	</question>
	
