	<question id="2012BeijingGaokao_20_02" type="shortanswer">
	    <text format="latex">$r_{1}(A)=1-2d$,$r_{2}(A)=-1+2d$,$c_{1}(A)=c_{2}(A)=1+d$,$c_{3}(A)=-2-2d$.因为$-1\leq d\leq 0$,所以$|r_{1}(A)|=|r_{2}(A)|\geq 1+d\geq 0$,$|c_{3}(A)|\geq 1+d\geq 0$.所以$k(A)=1+d\leq 0$.当$d=0$时,$k(A)$取得最大值1.</text>
